## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **opioid epidemic + antidote distribution** = naloxone OTC 2023 FDA approval (Narcan), public health impact 매우 큼. quantum-VQE 의 longer-acting / nasal-bioavailable 향상 path.
2. **acetaminophen overdose** = leading cause of acute liver failure US. NAC time-critical (within 8-10h ideal). quantum-design 외부.
3. **environmental toxicology** = air pollution PM2.5 의 mortality contribution 큼, 단 quantum 직접 X (regulatory + engineering).
4. **rattlesnake antivenom** = horse-derived (CroFab) 또는 sheep (Anavip 2015) — cost + access issue.
5. **DDI CYP450 prediction** — quantum-VQE 의 CYP3A4 binding affinity prediction 가능 (drug development 의 standard).
6. **heavy metal chelation** — Pb / As / Hg / Cd 각 specific chelator. quantum-design 의 selective chelator 가능.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, toxicology 임상 의미 한정.

